    "To illustrate the changes in F1 scores, we ultimately chose 1500 tokens and 3000 tokens to apply to all prompts.",
    "Meta Llama: Meta offers Llama as an open-source LLM.",
    "Llama comes in two main versions, with version 1 (V1) being released in February 2023, and version 2 (V2) in July of the same year.",
    "V1 offers model sizes of 7B, 13B, 33B, and 65B, and V2 provides sizes of 7B, 13B, and 70B.",
    "In this paper, fine-tuning was conducted using the 7B model from Llama V1 due to the hardware constraints of using larger models."
